# Agent workflow

- Do **not** use Cursor workspaces, multi-root setups, or `move_agent_to_cloned_root` / cloned checkouts. Stay in this repo.
- Always start new work on a **new branch** from updated `main` (e.g. `cursor/<topic>`). Do not pile new features onto a branch that already shipped or has a PR unless the user says to.
- Follow [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for the same rules.
